Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Frost/Nixon TV interviews, May 1977
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407cfr
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 May 1977
Frost/Nixon TV interviews. Compulsive viewing for massive US and UK audiences. Reveal Nixon's human failings. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less